  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5787487">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5787487/" class="title-link">透过有形的墓葬器具，探寻神秘的死亡世界</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5787487"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/49874773/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u49874773-11.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/49874773/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">海风</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-02-22"
      class="main-meta">2013-02-22 09:13:38</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5787487_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  古人对于生死的种种观念，都物化在这些具体的器具之上。透过它们，使我们得以一窥未知世界的奥秘。 我们一出生便走向这个世界，然而，我们对这个世界却一无所知。正因为无知，所以往往心怀恐惧。而对其进行文化上的探寻，让每个走到这一步的人会坦然面对。至少可以让艺术的光辉...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5787487_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5787487_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





